able 使用软件自动调整导出3种不同的结果，差别非常明显。在这种情况下，哪一种算是原片直出呢，原片直出又如何呢？","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":173,"offset":1479},"end":{"line":22,"column":335,"offset":1641}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1,"offset":1307},"end":{"line":22,"column":335,"offset":1641}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"image","title":null,"url":"/blog/photos/2020-03-14_compare-softwares.jpg","alt":"","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":1,"offset":1645},"end":{"line":24,"column":51,"offset":1695}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":1,"offset":1645},"end":{"line":24,"column":51,"offset":1695}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"那还有人问了，对于那些一眼就看出来是调过颜色的，而且颜色一看就是现实生活中看不到的搭配，那我是不是就可以开始喷了呢？当然也不是，如果大家都能看出图片的颜色不同于日常真实，说明这张图片就不是照片，而是作者基于照片的艺术创作。认为这样的图片应该反映真实，就好比把小说情节当作史料来引用一样，这不是小说作家的错误，理解一件作品是作者和观众两方面的责任。","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1,"offset":1699},"end":{"line":26,"column":174,"offset":1872}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1,"offset":1699},"end":{"line":26,"column":174,"offset":1872}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"如果以上这些依然不能说服对方，或者别人摆明了就是来砸场子的，那咱也不客气——","position":{"start":{"line":28,"column":1,"offset":1876},"end":{"line":28,"column":39,"offset":1914}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":28,"column":1,"offset":1876},"end":{"line":28,"column":39,"offset":1914}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"“您那巴掌大的屏幕做过色彩管理吗？能把颜色都显示准了吗？我这儿原片直出有用吗？颜色准不准您能看得出来吗？”","position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":1,"offset":1918},"end":{"line":30,"column":54,"offset":1971}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":1,"offset":1918},"end":{"line":30,"column":54,"offset":1971}}},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Adobe LightRoom、RawTherapy 和 DarkTable","position":{"start":{"line":32,"column":4,"offset":1978},"end":{"line":32,"column":42,"offset":2016}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":32,"column":1,"offset":1975},"end":{"line":32,"column":42,"offset":2016}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"我的手机上一直常备有 Adobe LightRoom 的移动版，免费版的功能够用，可以直接用软件控制相机的光圈快门等参数，拍摄 RAW 图像（","position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":1,"offset":2020},"end":{"line":34,"column":72,"offset":2091}}},{"type":"inlineCode","value":".dng","position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":72,"offset":2091},"end":{"line":34,"column":78,"offset":2097}}},{"type":"text","value":" 格式）。","position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":78,"offset":2097},"end":{"line":34,"column":83,"offset":2102}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":1,"offset":2020},"end":{"line":34,"column":83,"offset":2102}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"但是 Adobe 家的 PC 软件是要收费的，而且现在不是一锤子买卖，而是按月交保护费，让人感觉随时在接受剥削。前年圣诞节的时候有优惠，一口气交了一年的钱。但是过了一段时间之后，我忘了究竟交了多少钱，也就不知道是不是还在每月扣款，而且受到了开源自由软件精神的 ","position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1,"offset":2106},"end":{"line":36,"column":131,"offset":2236}}},{"type":"delete","children":[{"type":"text","value":"(洗脑)","position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":133,"offset":2238},"end":{"line":36,"column":137,"offset":2242}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":131,"offset":2236},"end":{"line":36,"column":139,"offset":2244}}},{"type":"text","value":" 感召，于是毅然退订了 Adobe 的服务 ","position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":139,"offset":2244},"end":{"line":36,"column":161,"offset":2266}}},{"type":"delete","children":[{"type":"text","value":"(然后发现钱已经交过了，退订意味着少了接近半年的服务，外加损失一个月的月费)","position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":163,"offset":2268},"end":{"line":36,"column":201,"offset":2306}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":161,"offset":2266},"end":{"line":36,"column":203,"offset":2308}}},{"type":"text","value":"。没了张屠夫，咱也不能吃带毛的猪啊，于是一番搜索，找到了 RawTherapy 和 DarkTable 两个替代产品。","position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":203,"offset":2308},"end":{"line":36,"column":262,"offset":2367}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1,"offset":2106},"end":{"line":36,"column":262,"offset":2367}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"在","position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1,"offset":2371},"end":{"line":38,"column":2,"offset":2372}}},{"type":"link","title":null,"url":"https://linux.cn/article-10912-1.html","children":[{"type":"text","value":"这篇文章","position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":3,"offset":2373},"end":{"line":38,"column":7,"offset":2377}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":2,"offset":2372},"end":{"line":38,"column":47,"offset":2417}}},{"type":"text","value":"的忽悠之下，我决定使用 RawTherapy，因为据文章说 DarkTable 对 Windows 版本的维护不如 Linux 上心。但是用了 RawTherapy 之后总觉得哪里不对，每次导入图片的时候都感觉“咦，怎么当时很漂亮的照片在电脑里看这么丑”，我又不是没见过 RAW 图片，这种反差实在是超出预期，而且使得修图的工作量大了很多。去年夏天，有个学妹来我们实验室访学，临走的时候我带她去动物园和博物馆逛了一天，回来之后看着成吨的废片，欲哭无泪……","position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":47,"offset":2417},"end":{"line":38,"column":274,"offset":2644}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1,"offset":2371},"end":{"line":38,"column":274,"offset":2644}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"今年冬天的第二场雪，我和新认识的老乡一起去城东边远郊的一个小村子拍雪景。回来之后不久，老乡就在微信公众号发了一篇游记，我则看了一眼图片文件夹就再也不想修图了，以至于拖延到现在。抱着死马当活马医的想法，下载了 DarkTable，然后发现几乎不怎么用调整就可以得到还算令人满意的效果（见上面的对比图）。对于 LightRoom，我最念念不忘的就是它 ","position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":1,"offset":2648},"end":{"line":40,"column":175,"offset":2822}}},{"type":"inlineCode","value":"Color Mix","position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":175,"offset":2822},"end":{"line":40,"column":186,"offset":2833}}},{"type":"text","value":" 的功能，在 DarkTable 中，","position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":186,"offset":2833},"end":{"line":40,"column":205,"offset":2852}}},{"type":"inlineCode","value":"Color Zone","position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":205,"offset":2852},"end":{"line":40,"column":217,"offset":2864}}},{"type":"text","value":" 和 ","position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":217,"offset":2864},"end":{"line":40,"column":220,"offset":2867}}},{"type":"inlineCode","value":"Color Look Up Table","position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":220,"offset":2867},"end":{"line":40,"column":241,"offset":2888}}},{"type":"text","value":" 两个功能基本上可以取代。情况没有什么变化的话，我应该会在将来一直使用 DarkTable 了。","position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":241,"offset":2888},"end":{"line":40,"column":289,"offset":2936}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":1,"offset":2648},"end":{"line":40,"column":289,"offset":2936}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"image","title":null,"url":"/blog/photos/2020-03-14_lightroom-darktable.jpg","alt":"","position":{"start":{"line":42,"column":1,"offset":2940},"end":{"line":42,"column":53,"offset":2992}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":42,"column":1,"offset":2940},"end":{"line":42,"column":53,"offset":2992}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"事实证明网上的测评文章几乎没什么用，哪怕作者没有被开发者收买，也不一定有能正确描述不同软件异同的洞察力和表达力，而且结论还往往基于一些没有明言的个人经验和价值观。所以也请不要把这篇文章看作是 RawTherapy 和 DarkTable 的严肃测评，只是我对自己使用经历和感受的一段叙述。如果你也觉得其中一款用起来很不顺手，可以考虑换一个试用一段时间。","position":{"start":{"line":44,"column":1,"offset":2996},"end":{"line":44,"column":177,"offset":3172}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":44,"column":1,"offset":2996},"end":{"line":44,"column":177,"offset":3172}}},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"children":[{"type":"text","value":"说回这次的照片","position":{"start":{"line":46,"column":4,"offset":3179},"end":{"line":46,"column":11,"offset":3186}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":46,"column":1,"offset":3176},"end":{"line":46,"column":11,"offset":3186}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"上个学期隔壁实验室有一个学弟在做 rotation，正好当时他们老板和我们老板 ","position":{"start":{"line":48,"column":1,"offset":3190},"end":{"line":48,"column":41,"offset":3230}}},{"type":"delete","children":[{"type":"text","value":"（情投意合）","position":{"start":{"line":48,"column":43,"offset":3232},"end":{"line":48,"column":49,"offset":3238}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":48,"column":41,"offset":3230},"end":{"line":48,"column":51,"offset":3240}}},{"type":"text","value":" 志同道合，于是就有一个合作的小项目。互相加了一下微信之后，翻了翻他的朋友圈，发现居然是老乡，还是同一高中的校友，而且也有一个个人向的微信公众号，于是相约有时间一起出去拍照片。","position":{"start":{"line":48,"column":51,"offset":3240},"end":{"line":48,"column":139,"offset":3328}}},{"type":"delete","children":[{"type":"text","value":"（啊，社会工程学是多么地可怕）","position":{"start":{"line":48,"column":141,"offset":3330},"end":{"line":48,"column":156,"offset":3345}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":48,"column":139,"offset":3328},"end":{"line":48,"column":158,"offset":3347}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":48,"column":1,"offset":3190},"end":{"line":48,"column":158,"offset":3347}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"今年冬天气候有点怪，开始降温的过程非常平滑缓慢，而且气温一直不低。然后一次突如其来的降温带来一次突如其来的大雪，等到反应过来的时候已经化的差不多了。冬天里的雪就像经济危机里的股灾一样，有了第一次暴跌就有第二次 :-)，于是第二次的时候，我们抓住机会来了一次逃学威龙，来到城西的一个小县城里看雪。","position":{"start":{"line":50,"column":1,"offset":3351},"end":{"line":50,"column":148,"offset":3498}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":50,"column":1,"offset":3351},"end":{"line":50,"column":148,"offset":3498}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"然后，这就是这次我最满意的一张照片了。","position":{"start":{"line":52,"column":1,"offset":3502},"end":{"line":52,"column":20,"offset":3521}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":52,"column":1,"offset":3502},"end":{"line":52,"column":20,"offset":3521}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"处理的方法也很简单，DarkTable 的直方图可以直接拖动，而且最暗的四分之一和较亮的部分可以分开处理，所以就直接把直方图的右半边往右拉，左边往左拉，使得一部分的像素过曝，同时一部分的暗部完全压暗成黑色。这样做是因为看到图片中最白的像素一定来自雪，而黑色来自树皮上的皴裂，将两者的色彩对比拉开之后，图片自然就会显得通透，也符合尽可以贴近自己眼前所见的原则。另外色彩的饱和度稍微提高一些，为了避免过于鲜艳，把对比度稍微降低一些，但是这些操作对于整体效果的影响不大。","position":{"start":{"line":54,"column":1,"offset":3525},"end":{"line":54,"column":233,"offset":3757}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":54,"column":1,"offset":3525},"end":{"line":54,"column":233,"offset":3757}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"image","title":null,"url":"/blog/photos/2020-03-14_comparison.png","alt":"","position":{"start":{"line":56,"column":1,"offset":3761},"end":{"line":56,"column":44,"offset":3804}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":56,"column":1,"offset":3761},"end":{"line":56,"column":44,"offset":3804}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1,"offset":0},"end":{"line":59,"column":1,"offset":3810}}},"htmlAst":{"type":"root","children":[